f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係貪佢人工高又有時間hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> probation未過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到高層少少既都好懷疑我既能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e569bb9fddf1b6f762828f002c9416c7a4f08368","tid":1487644,"uid":75637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"我一開始返而家呢份工都成日做錯野，之後決定攞本notebook抄低同事教過嘅野 ，同埋自己錯過嘅野，當下次再做嗰陣就攞本notebook出黎望，睇吓有冇咩地方又做錯 ，確保自己唔好再錯<br />\n另外真係驚的話，就返工前一晚/開工前睇熟d notes , 自己腦入面run 一run做野個workflow, 等自己做野smooth d, 自自然然就會減少緊張做錯嘅機會，粗心大意呢樣野係可以改善的，如果你因為驚粗心大意而辭職，你去到第二份工都係會粗心大意，所以最好係要改變自己，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b299a7046accd25be989db88b5d00e0b8946a22c","tid":1487644,"uid":266336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a3b194cd2a77da93cb6f85160582ef7e845a3ec","tid":1487644,"uid":270528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"唉。上手好慢、唔係話頭醒尾、一樣野做幾10次都有機會錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日唔小心整錯公司啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實唔係直接關我事，但係好大機會同事以為係我整錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢份工要準確度好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我咁樣到底係唔適合份工定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"準確度好高嘅工真心大頭蝦嘅人唔好做,影響好大,如果係日常生活服務果啲,仲危險<br />\nbtw 你並不孤單,因為我都係上手好慢、唔係話頭醒尾果類人(但我信力求改進,勝於一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"e2433582025cdbb19f3ccfbfa22d7e740322f09f","tid":1487644,"uid":270528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e569bb9fddf1b6f762828f002c9416c7a4f08368","tid":1487644,"uid":75637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"我一開始返而家呢份工都成日做錯野，之後決定攞本notebook抄低同事教過嘅野 ，同埋自己錯過嘅野，當下次再做嗰陣就攞本notebook出黎望，睇吓有冇咩地方又做錯 ，確保自己唔好再錯<br />\n另外真係驚的話，就返工前一晚/開工前睇熟d notes , 自己腦入面run 一run做野個workflow, 等自己做野smooth d, 自自然然就會減少緊張做錯嘅機會，粗心大意呢樣野係可以改善的，如果你因為驚粗心大意而辭職，你去到第二份工都係會粗心大意，所以最好係要改變自己，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時有同事會話hand on experience 重要過你係咁抄抄抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見抄完又係錯都唔知佢地咩觀感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時有同事講過1次，然後佢自己唔記得左，話講左4次我都唔記得有無搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8606503e379bbe5e496a62366aa8853f78c7bda","tid":1487644,"uid":126884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a97660ddc64ab407e0996c9a18c47ddc47933a","tid":1487644,"uid":270528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fce9b5c13ebc60f1b7567dc4ec2f9da2fbc8dabf","tid":1487644,"uid":65858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你根本對份工一啲啲興趣都冇<br />\n下意識覺得啲野無聊冇用 覺得唔需要睇/記<br />\n試下轉工/將興趣變成工作啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係對份工一啲興趣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係貪佢人工高又有時間hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> probation未過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到高層少少既都好懷疑我既能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"如果想自己上心d<br />\n可以嘗試下set 一d 工作目標同standard 俾自己 （要係量化到）<br />\ni.e. 用指定時間做某一個項目既工作"},{"pid":"a48a999f7a13d47bd5f868bcb8d9c6362b035887","tid":1487644,"uid":126884