\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢份工要準確度好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我咁樣到底係唔適合份工定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"我之前返文職 成日入資料落電腦都入漏野/打錯字<br />\nFILING果陣又係成日10樣野MISS咁1/2樣<br />\n有時自己PROOFREADING完先交比上司都重有野錯<br />\n最尾做夠一年就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"成日帶漏公司文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"同事有無話你"},{"pid":"00337affdb7f28070bd832a9f34f98a2e981f714","tid":1487644,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準確呢啲係最基本要求"},{"pid":"c3fd751889de5a31a212630177497e7e5350ce37","tid":1487644,"uid":123431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"如果新入職，我需要大概講一次比我聽我抄低，然後搵一次一路做一路講比我聽，然後我自己做一次比同事check.我覺得呢個先係完整學習既過程。 <br />\n但好多同事覺得講一次就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果講一次就全部識曬，兼無做錯，我可以做senior 坐你個位啦"},{"pid":"ebae5dc94596ba0edf9044ffb159d90771f71948","tid":1487644,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a97660ddc64ab407e0996c9a18c47ddc47933a","tid":1487644,"uid":270528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fce9b5c13ebc60f1b7567dc4ec2f9da2fbc8dabf","tid":1487644,"uid":65858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你根本對份工一啲啲興趣都冇<br />\n下意識覺得啲野無聊冇用 覺得唔需要睇/記<br />\n試下轉工/將興趣變成工作啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係對份工一啲興趣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 